Package: clusterpath
Type: Package
Title: Fast agglomerative clustering using convex fusion penalties
Version: 1.1
Date: 2011-05-10
Author: Toby Dylan Hocking
Maintainer: Toby Dylan Hocking <toby.hocking@inria.fr>
Description: Implements the clusterpath, a clustering method in which all
 the clusters are solutions to a convex optimization problem with fusion
 penalties. This package is a wrapper around the C++ implementation.
License: GPL-3
LazyLoad: yes
Depends: R (>= 2.14.0), Rcpp (>= 0.8.0), lattice, ggplot2, plyr, reshape2, 
	 latticeExtra, Matrix, grid
Suggests: rgl, directlabels, mclust, multicore
LinkingTo: Rcpp
SystemRequirements: GNU make
